  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Whilst I appreciate that there are installable ones available, a native one which you can rely on when you remote into any server (as long as the version of PS is up to date) would be much better. \r\n \r\nI cannot install apps I want on a remote server without a long approval process, so a built in one would be much more useful. \r\n\r\nI don't even care about syntax highlighting, just being able to change some text in remote config files would be a huge help. ",
